name: FoodAndNutritionRelatedHistoryLOINC
title: Food and Nutrition Related History LOINC
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Food and nutrition history of an individual as recorded by a nutrition professional as a component of a Nutrition Assessment.),(Data Element Scope: Food and nutrition related history includes items such as, food and nutrient intake, meal and snack patterns, and their eating environment.),(Inclusion Criteria: Data included is nutrition history assessment data used to determine an individualized nutrition care plan by a nutrition professional.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes other aspects of nutrition assessment, such as, lab values, anthropometrics, client history. It also excludes nutrition diagnoses (problems) and nutrition intervention care planning.)
